To run this program we need to compail two file

make all

We will run first the server 

./server

And then the client with three arguments, pid of the server, signal number and the number of time we want to sent the signals or print

./client <server pid> number_of_signal number_of_times

When the server is running, his pid print in the terminal.
This pid we need to write when we run the client.

